.hero
  = image_tag "hero.jpg", class: "full-width"
  = image_tag "everybody_wins.png", class: "everybody"

.row.columns.content
  .row.collapse
    .columns.small-12.large-9
      %h1 The race could go either way. Register today to ensure Donald's defeat.

      %p.xlarge-txt.subheader
        Register with your state and desired candidate. In October, (if appropriate) we'll match you with a
        voter in a different state to trade votes with.
        = link_to "Read more.", about_path
    .columns.small-12.large-3.text-center.large-text-left.margin-top-1
      = link_to "Count me in!", new_user_registration_path, class: "button xlarge"

  .row
    .columns.small-12.medium-6.end
      %ul.checkboxes
        %li
          Hillary Clinton wins critical swing states.
        %li
          Third-party candidates receive more votes overall, giving them a better chance of reaching critical federal thresholds.

  .row.collapse
    .columns.small-12.medium-8.large-6.medium-centered
      = image_tag "arrow-right.svg", class: "left left-arrow"
      %h5.text-center.margin-top-1
        %span.color-primary TELEPORT YOUR VOTE
        %span.color-tertiary TO A STATE WHERE IT MATTERS.
  .row.collapse
    .columns.small-12
      = image_tag "teleport-no-words.svg", class: "full-width"
  .row.collapse
    .columns.small-12.medium-8.large-6.medium-centered
      = image_tag "arrow-right.svg", class: "right"
      %h5.text-center
        %span.color-primary TELEPORT YOUR VOTE
        %span.color-tertiary TO A STATE WHERE IT WON'T INDIRECTLY HELP
        %span.color-secondary TRUMP
        %span.color-tertiary WIN.


  .row
    .columns.small-12.medium-6.medium-centered.margin-top-2.margin-bottom-2
      %p.large-txt.text-justify
        By strategically trading votes with voters in other states, we can have our cake and eat it too.
        Third-party candidates get more votes, and Hillary Clinton wins.

  .row
    .columns.small-12.medium-6.medium-centered
      = image_tag "everybody-wins-black.png"

